data.description: This beautiful limestone block, custom-built 2 story home is in a quiet established neighborhood with no through traffic adjacent to a cul-de-sac.  Downstairs features include high ceilings, open concept floor plan, recessed lighting and 2 living areas - one with a wood burning fireplace.  The kitchen sports a large island wonderful for serving and entertaining, walk in pantry and granite countertops. The master bath includes granite countertops with double vanities, a spacious double headed walk-in shower and a large walk-in closet.  A nice staircase leads to 3 additional bedrooms with a jack and jill bath.  One bedroom accesses a balcony overlooking the front of the home.  The back of the home opens to a covered patio and nice size yard.  The side yard contains a fenced-in dog run and a sprinkler system services the front yard.
